'''赤腹山雀'''(''Sittiparus castaneoventris'')是[[山雀科|山雀科]]的一種小型鳥類，為台灣特有種。

最初由英國鳥類學家[[約翰古爾德|約翰古爾德]]( John Gould)於1863年首次描述，並定其學名為''Parus castaneoventris''.<ref>{{cite journal | last=Gould | first=John | author-link=John Gould | year=1863 | title=Descriptions of sixteen new species of birds from the island of Formosa, collected by Robert Swinhoe, Esq., her Majesty's Vice-Consul at Formosa | journal=Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London | issue=3 | page=280 | url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/31577324 | access-date=2019-03-29 | archive-date=2021-02-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225165211/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/31577324 | dead-url=no }} The title page gives the year as 1862.</ref> 以前被認為是[[雜色山雀|雜色山雀]]的[[亞種|亞種]]，但在2014年[[種系發生學|種系發生學]]研究發表後被提升為新物種。<ref name=mckay>{{cite journal | last1=McKay  | first1=B.D. | last2=Mays Jnr | first2=H.L. | last3=Tao | first3=C.-T. | last4=Wan | first4=D. | last5=Higuchi | first5=H. | last6=Nishium | first6=I. | year=2014 | title=Incorporating color into integrative taxonomy: analysis of the Varied Tit (''Sittiparus varius'') complex in East Asia | journal=Systems Biology | volume=63 | issue=4 | pages=505–517 | doi=10.1093/sysbio/syu016 }}</ref><ref name=ioc>{{cite web | editor1-last=Gill | editor1-first=Frank | editor2-last=Donsker | editor2-first=David | title=Waxwings and their allies, tits & penduline tits | work=World Bird List Version 6.1 | url=http://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/waxwings/ | publisher=International Ornithologists' Union | accessdate=15 February 2016 | archive-date=2014-05-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506103507/http://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/waxwings/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

此種與[[雜色山雀|雜色山雀]]的不同之處，在於其身體下半部是深栗色的。<ref name=hbwalive>{{cite web| last1=Gosler| first1=A. | last2=Clement | first2=P. | year=2017 | title=Varied Tit (''Sittiparus varius'') | editor1-last=del Hoyo | editor1-first=J. | editor2-last=Elliott | editor2-first=A. | editor3-last=Sargatal | editor3-first=J. | editor4-last=Christie | editor4-first=D.A. | editor5-last=de Juana | editor5-first=E. | work=Handbook of the Birds of the World Alive | publisher=Lynx Edicions | url=http://www.hbw.com/node/59870  | accessdate=2 September 2017}}{{subscription required}}</ref>

